<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/favicon.png">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@600&family=Open+Sans:wght@500&family=Poppins:wght@600&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/home.css">
    <title>Hotel Website</title>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="wrapper">

        <div class="nav">
            <div class="left-section">
                <img src="./images/logo.png" alt="logo" height="60" width="60">
                <h2 id="heading"><a href="#">Imperial Crown Hotel</a></h2>
            </div>
            <div class="right-section">
                <ul>
                    <li>Home</li>
                    <li>About</li>
                    <li>Rooms</li>
                    <li>Pages</li>
                </ul>
                <button class="nav-btn">Book Now</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="main">
            <div class="inner">
                <h1>Spend Your Holidays</h1>
                <p>Escape, relax, and rejuvenate in our exquisite holiday haven.</p>
                <div>
                    <button class="btn" id="read">READ MORE</button>
                    <button class="btn" id="contact">CONTACT US</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h3 id="aboutt">About</h3>
        <div class="about">
            <div class="left-about">
                <h3>Imperial Crown Hotel</h3>
                <p>Welcome to the Imperial Crown Hotel, an oasis of luxury and refinement. Established in [2022], our
                    hotel embodies timeless elegance, offering lavish accommodations, exquisite dining, and impeccable
                    service. Nestled in the heart of [Location], our legacy of hospitality awaits, inviting you to
                    experience a harmonious blend of regal charm and modern comfort. Your journey into opulence begins
                    here.</p>
                <button class="btn" id="about-btn">ABOUT US</button>
            </div>
            <div class="right-about">
                <img src="./images/about.jpg" alt="about">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rooms-heading">
            <h3>Our Rooms</h3>
            <p>Discover opulent comfort in our rooms – where luxury meets tranquility. Your retreat awaits.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rooms">
            <div class="cards">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="./images/room1.jpg" alt="room1" height="300" width="300">
                    <h4>Standard Room</h4> 
                    <p>Comfortable and well-equipped standard room for a relaxing stay.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="./images/room2.jpg" alt="room2" height="300" width="300">
                    <h4>Family Room</h4>
                    <p>Spacious family retreat with amenities for a memorable shared experience.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="./images/room3.jpg" alt="room2" height="300" width="300">
                    <h4>Deluxe Room</h4>
                    <p>Elegant and spacious deluxe room for a luxurious, comfortable experience.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="services-heading">
            <h3>Services</h3>
            <p>Pamper yourself with our exquisite services – from spa indulgence to personalized concierge.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="services">
            <div class="inner-services">
                <div class="grid">
                    <img src="images/food.jpg" alt="">
                    <h5>Food</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="grid">
                    <img src="./images/fitness.jpg" alt="">
                    <h5>Fitness</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="grid">
                    <img src="./images/inhouseres.jpg" alt="">
                    <h5>Inhouse Restaurant</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="grid">
                    <img src="./images/beautyspa.jpg" alt="">
                    <h5>Beauty Spa</h5>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="footer-logo">
                    <img src="./images/logo.png" alt="Logo" height="40" width="40">
                    <h2>Imperial Crown Hotel</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-links">
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Rooms</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Services</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-contact">
                    <p>Email: inperial@gmail.com</p>
                    <p>Phone: +123 456 7890</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <p>&copy; 2024 Imperial Crown Hotel. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>

</html>